profile: For over 40 years, we have helped Ontario homeowners and builders build safer, more energy-efficient and sustainable communities. With a broad range of products and services, we are your insulation experts for existing home renovation upgrades and new residential home construction—satisfaction guaranteed. Proudly serving all of Southern Ontario, we are Ontario's largest insulation company and are Energy Star and Foam Masters™ certified. Get in touch for a Free In-Home Assessment—contact us today to learn more.

profile: Attic Insulations With over THIRTY-FOUR years in business, Knox Insulation & Roofing has built an enviable reputation by employing fully licensed professionals, and by utilizing quality industry recognized products, and also by providing the highest level of service resulting in total customer satisfaction. Whether your home improvement plans include attics, garages, roofs, or walls, Knox Insulation & Roofing has the expertise to provide you with permanent energy savings. Also, Knox Insulation & Roofing will provide all the information necessary for you to take advantage of the numerous government rebates currently available. These government-assisted programs allow Ontario residents to permanently reduce energy costs, while helping to promote overall energy conservation programs. profile:
As our tagline says “we will make your house a home” we always believe it starts with a warm environment, it’s our way of helping to improve communities and help relieve the stress of home owning. We truly believe that it’s not just about insulation, it’s about creating a comfortable home, comfortable living, building a community and helping families feel secure. It’s the welcoming feeling of coming home to a warm house in the winter and a cool house in the summer. 

This is where we got inspired to want to provide insulation to homes and businesses and with that backing it helps us carry through on our best quality of service.  We believe we are going to live up to the standard of our vision of that welcome home feeling.
